data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Bartlett, TN! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is nestled in a beautiful walkable neighborhood, offering an easy retreat from the hustle and bustle. The spacious living area is perfect for both relaxation and entertaining guests.  One of the highlights of this home is the refreshing pool, inviting you to cool off during hot Tennessee summers. Imagine spending lazy weekends enjoying the pool or hosting gatherings with friends and family.
